  "texts": [
    "Of the 150 non-redundant Ae.",
    "tauschii L2 accessions, we could assign 133 to one of the four L2 subpopulations on the basis of an ancestry threshold of greater than or equal to 70% (Supplementary Table 3).",
    "The remaining 17 L2 accessions were considered admixed.",
    "Using genetic, geographical and phenotypic diversity, we selected 46 accessions to construct high-quality genome assemblies, comprising 11 L1 accessions, 34 L2 accessions and 1 L3 accession (Fig. 1a,b and Supplementary Table 4).",
    "The 46 accessions captured 72.5% of the genetic diversity present in the Ae."
  ],
